Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> program
Rule 1     program -> statements
Rule 2     block -> LBRACE statements RBRACE
Rule 3     statement -> declaration
Rule 4     statement -> assignment
Rule 5     statement -> print_stmt
Rule 6     statement -> if_stmt
Rule 7     statement -> while_stmt
Rule 8     statements -> statements statement
Rule 9     statements -> statement
Rule 10    statement -> BREAK SEMICOLON
Rule 11    statement -> CONTINUE SEMICOLON
Rule 12    declaration -> INT ID ASSIGN expression SEMICOLON
Rule 13    assignment -> ID ASSIGN expression SEMICOLON
Rule 14    print_stmt -> PRINTF LPAREN expression RPAREN SEMICOLON
Rule 15    if_stmt -> IF LPAREN expression RPAREN block
Rule 16    if_stmt -> IF LPAREN expression RPAREN block ELSE block
Rule 17    while_stmt -> WHILE LPAREN expression RPAREN block
Rule 18    expression -> expression PLUS expression
Rule 19    expression -> expression MINUS expression
Rule 20    expression -> expression TIMES expression
Rule 21    expression -> expression DIVIDE expression
Rule 22    expression -> expression GT expression
Rule 23    expression -> expression LT expression
Rule 24    expression -> expression GE expression
Rule 25    expression -> expression LE expression
Rule 26    expression -> expression EQ expression
Rule 27    expression -> expression NE expression
Rule 28    expression -> NUMBER
Rule 29    expression -> ID

